{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji27.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给张四维的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给张四维的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年11月17日）长沙福寿桥三号张四维先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未阳电悉，甚感好意。湖南需才孔急，似以在当地工作为宜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]张四维（1892—1961），湖南省韶山市韶山乡韶山村人。大革命时期曾参加韶山农民运动。新中国成立后，在中国盐业公司湖南省公司工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]旧时人们在电报中常以地支代月、韵目代日的方法表示发报时间。未阳，即8月7日。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":522,"page_end":522},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}